Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.60,default,,0,0,0,,It's the final match\Nof E-Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.15,0:00:58.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,Ｅカード 最終戦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:00.84,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji is at his wit's end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:00.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ 絶体絶命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.84,0:01:04.74,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Enforcement
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:16.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざわ… ざわ… ざわざわざわ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:25.86,default,,0,0,0,,You're dead! Your switching of\Nthe cards wasn't successful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:24.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んだ！お前のわな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:28.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すり替えは実らない 殺した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:27.23,default,,0,0,0,,I killed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.91,0:01:31.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皇帝で！ハハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:30.40,default,,0,0,0,,...with the Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.58,0:01:32.50,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:36.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川 俺が蛇に見えたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:35.94,default,,0,0,0,,Do you see me as a snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.44,default,,0,0,0,,You're a snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:38.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蛇だろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.07,default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:43.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか なら… お前が蛇なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:43.31,default,,0,0,0,,In that case,\N you are the snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:45.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:44.31,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな もの言わぬカードを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,使っての心理戦は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:48.58,default,,0,0,0,,A psychological battle that uses\Nambiguous cards like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:50.82,default,,0,0,0,,...is like looking into\Na mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:51.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鏡をのぞき込むようなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相手の心を読んでいるつもりが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.09,default,,0,0,0,,You plan to read your\Nopponent's mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:57.08,default,,0,0,0,,but you end up putting\Nyourself in his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分ならどうするかという
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:57.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自己への問いかけとなり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:01.36,default,,0,0,0,,Before you know it, you're just\Ntracing your own thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:01.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気付けば ただ自分の心を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:02:01.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぞっているだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:07.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 俺が蛇に見えた お前こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:07.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蛇なんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:06.16,default,,0,0,0,,So if you think I'm a snake,\Nthen you're also one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:12.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがどうした 見苦しい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.84,default,,0,0,0,,So what about it?\NHow disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:14.31,default,,0,0,0,,Just die!\NI don't want to hear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:15.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう死ね 聞きたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:19.08,default,,0,0,0,,Spending your last moments\Ncrying shamelessly and cursing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:19.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後のときに ぐずぐずと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:19.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,醜い泣き言 恨み言など
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.63,default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:23.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや そんなんじゃない 礼さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:22.82,default,,0,0,0,,I'm thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,礼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.15,default,,0,0,0,,Thank me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:27.65,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蛇で いてくれて ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:34.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,疑ってくれて ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:34.16,default,,0,0,0,,And thank you for\Nbeing suspicious of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:03.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷は ２度刺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.62,default,,0,0,0,,The Slave strikes again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くー やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:14.13,default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:20.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝った！勝った！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.45,default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:26.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごいっすよ！カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.72,default,,0,0,0,,Alright! He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:26.15,default,,0,0,0,,Alright! He really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.13,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん やったね！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.15,default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect you to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に すごいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか勝てるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:34.55,default,,0,0,0,,You're incredible!\NIncredible! Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:35.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごい すごいよ カイジさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:42.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな… そんな ばかな！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:40.79,default,,0,0,0,,This is... this is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:46.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして奴隷 どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:45.46,default,,0,0,0,,Why is it the Slave... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:51.00,default,,0,0,0,,Hadn't he switched the cards?\NHe'd bled on them then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:50.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すり替えたんじゃないのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.15,0:03:50.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき 血が飛び散る前に！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ… んん… んんっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.38,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.22,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:12.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すり替えたんじゃないのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.75,default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you swap the cards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:17.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残念だが そうじゃねえのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.79,default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに その時間はあった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:19.77,default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I had enough time\Nto do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:24.04,default,,0,0,0,,And while I did something similar,\NI didn't switch the cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして それに近いことはしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すり替えは しなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.07,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.29,0:04:29.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がしたのは 血が飛び散る前に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:29.35,default,,0,0,0,,What I did was...\Nbefore splattering the blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:34.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,11戦で使った市民と奴隷を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:34.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手元に引き寄せ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.60,default,,0,0,0,,I moved the Citizen and Slave\Ncards from the 11th round...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.06,default,,0,0,0,,...into my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.54,default,,0,0,0,,Then I placed a Citizen card\Nnext to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その横に ただ市民を置き
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:41.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その市民をそのまま手に戻した
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:39.82,default,,0,0,0,,and returned the Citizen card\Nback into my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:44.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すり替えもどき それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.22,default,,0,0,0,,I pretended to switch\Nthe cards, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:45.50,default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばかな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな ばかなことがあるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:48.13,default,,0,0,0,,How could such an impossible\Nthing happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:52.96,default,,0,0,0,,What if I had only noticed the\Nblood, but didn't suspect you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:53.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが血に気付いただけで その後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:53.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,疑わなかったら どうするんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしがカードの血を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただのミスとしか見なかったら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:56.40,default,,0,0,0,,What if I saw the blood as\Njust a mistake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:00.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は ただ無為に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:00.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしに奴隷の目印だけを与えて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:05:01.28,default,,0,0,0,,You'd have simply marked out\Nthe Slave for me and died!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:05.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死… 死んでいたじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.40,default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you have died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:06.94,default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:11.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして お前は…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.51,default,,0,0,0,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:16.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ… んんん…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:12.73,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:22.09,default,,0,0,0,,That's simple...\NI trusted you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:22.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単さ 俺は信頼したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何？信頼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.54,0:05:24.83,default,,0,0,0,,What? Trust...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.33,default,,0,0,0,,That's right. No matter how much\Nthe director complained about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこの会長が どう毒づこうと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.83,default,,0,0,0,,I think highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は あんたを買っている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:34.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,優秀だ それも とびっきり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:33.61,default,,0,0,0,,You're exceptional,\Nand have been so by far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:38.15,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way such a man\Nwouldn't notice the blood first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:37.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな男が まず この血に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:37.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気付かないはずがない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.93,default,,0,0,0,,With your talent,\Nyou'd surely notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:43.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気付くさ 優秀なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:47.45,default,,0,0,0,,And you wouldn't just believe\Nit was a honest mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:47.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気付いたら その血をそのまま
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:47.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単純に信じたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:52.58,default,,0,0,0,,You'd try to read my mind...\Nand see through my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:52.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず洞察する 見抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:52.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらの作為を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.94,0:05:54.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,優秀なんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:57.82,default,,0,0,0,,Because you're exceptional,\Nyou'd start to suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:58.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,優秀だから 気付いた後に疑うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:01.13,default,,0,0,0,,You'll start to draw your\Nown conclusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:02.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして その洞察は きっと届く
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:04.73,default,,0,0,0,,That I had the chance to\Nswitch the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すり替えのチャンスが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あったことに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに たどりつけば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:10.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の疑わしい動きにも気付き
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:11.37,default,,0,0,0,,And when you believe that, you'll\Ndetect my suspicious behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほくそ笑む このばかめと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.11,default,,0,0,0,,You'd think what\Na moron I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:17.59,default,,0,0,0,,and so you wouldn't\Nquestion your own victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:17.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:17.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう自分の勝ちを疑わない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:22.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃそうだ なんせ 今
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:22.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が相手にしてるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:22.35,default,,0,0,0,,And why not? After all,\Nthe person opposite you is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:26.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くず… ごみ… 劣等…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:26.05,default,,0,0,0,,Trash, garbage and second-class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:29.32,default,,0,0,0,,You'd think an outstanding person\Nlike you wouldn't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:30.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,優秀な自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:30.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか敗れるなんて思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:34.40,default,,0,0,0,,You would become arrogant\Nsince you know you're exceptional...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:34.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おごる おごるさ 優秀だから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.83,default,,0,0,0,,...simply because you've been\Nwinning all the while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:41.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで くずを寄せつけず
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.69,0:06:41.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ち続けてきたんだから！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:41.33,default,,0,0,0,,which sets yourself apart\Nfrom the garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:56.41,default,,0,0,0,,And so, the final round of E-Card\Ncomes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:56.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,12戦に及ぶＥカードは終了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:07:01.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは 勝負こそ５勝７敗と
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:07:01.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負け越したものの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:07:01.28,default,,0,0,0,,Though Kaiji recorded\N7 defeats and only 5 victories,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:05.96,default,,0,0,0,,due to his double 18 mm victories\Nin the final two rounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラスト２戦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,奴隷での18ミリ勝負の連勝が効き
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実質的には勝利で終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.64,default,,0,0,0,,he emerged as the overall winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.23,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji managed to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは生き残り
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.00,default,,0,0,0,,And he receives his reward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして得る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.00,default,,0,0,0,,A huge sum of 20.1 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:17.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大金2010万円！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:26.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハ… すばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.01,default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:31.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君が 実に すばらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:29.75,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, you're really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:37.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに比べて この男は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:37.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんだ恥さらし 醜態だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:37.49,default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, this man\Nis a complete disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 許されぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.56,default,,0,0,0,,He'll definitely not\Nbe forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:42.99,default,,0,0,0,,You will pay\Nfor your mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:43.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,してもらうぞ 償いだけは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.49,default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:47.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっちりとな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.00,default,,0,0,0,,Now then, Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:52.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて カイジ君 確か
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:52.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金を得て終わりではなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.60,default,,0,0,0,,I remember the reward wasn't\Nthe end of the deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ そうだ！利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土下座だ！謝ってもらうぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.47,default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NTonegawa, kneel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:08:00.05,default,,0,0,0,,I'll want you to apologise Ishida,\NSahara and the rest who died!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでいった石田さんや
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原たちに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:04.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってないな カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.47,default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.21,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:10.97,default,,0,0,0,,Humans will kneel when they\Nhave to in times of need...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:11.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間 いよいよとなれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:11.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頭など いくらでも下げる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題なのは その行為ではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:16.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誠意だろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:15.67,default,,0,0,0,,The problem doesn't lie with\Ndoing it. It's the sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:19.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹の底から謝っているか どうかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:19.46,default,,0,0,0,,Are they apologising from\Nthe bottom of their hearts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.62,0:08:21.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誠意？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.12,default,,0,0,0,,Sincerity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら床に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,額をこすりつけようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:24.84,default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many\Ntimes he kowtows,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:27.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹ん中で 舌を出されていては
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:27.74,default,,0,0,0,,if he's mocking you\Nin his heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死んでいった なんとかいう連中も
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,浮かばれは せんだろう？カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:31.17,default,,0,0,0,,the dead won't rest\Nin peace too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:31.97,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.80,0:08:34.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃまあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.57,default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:42.35,default,,0,0,0,,I know very well how meaningless\Nkneeling down can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは 身にしみているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土下座の無意味さについて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹の底からな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.64,default,,0,0,0,,From the bottom of\Nmy heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.65,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,How about it? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは 困ってる人間に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,拝み倒されると
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:51.35,default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't just ignore those people\Nwho are pleading with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:51.73,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Please! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:54.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見捨てることができず
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.12,0:08:54.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次々に金を貸し続けてきたのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:54.36,default,,0,0,0,,so I continued to lend\Nthem money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:56.13,default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:57.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けてやりたくてな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:01.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 結果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:09:01.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,煮え湯を飲まされ続けてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.96,default,,0,0,0,,However, in the end I just ended up\Nbeing cheated again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:05.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お互いの同意の上で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:05.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,契約したにも関わらず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:05.94,default,,0,0,0,,They ignore the contracts signed\Nin agreement by both parties,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:11.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いざ返す段になると
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:11.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,平然と踏み倒してくる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:10.22,default,,0,0,0,,and drag their feet when\Nthe time comes for repayment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:16.62,default,,0,0,0,,Of course they looked apologetic\Nand kowtowed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:13.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無論 表面上は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:13.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すまなそうな顔をして
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:18.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,床に額をこすりつけはするが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:21.30,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Please wait another 3 days,\NI beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:22.49,default,,0,0,0,,They thought why didn't this man\Nforgive them despite their apologies?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:22.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして これほど謝っているのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:22.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは許してくれないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,などと 心中 こちらを非難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:29.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冷血漢呼ばわりしてくるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:27.73,default,,0,0,0,,They blamed me, and called\Nme a cold-blooded man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.96,default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think\Nthat's a terrible story?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひどい話だと思わないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 そんな連中の わびに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誠意があるはずもない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:36.47,default,,0,0,0,,Of course, those people weren't\Nsincere in apologising at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一 借金における誠意なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:40.19,default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, no matter\Nhow you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:43.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはもう 誰が考えたって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:43.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つしかないのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:43.48,default,,0,0,0,,there's only one way to show your\Nsincerity towards your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:49.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち 何をしてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:49.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,期日までに金を返すことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:44.71,default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.61,default,,0,0,0,,they are free to do\Nanything they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.18,default,,0,0,0,,as long as they repay\Nthe money by the deadline!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:56.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以外に誠意などない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:54.53,default,,0,0,0,,There can be no other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:10:01.58,default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they can't be sincere\Nif they don't repay their debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:10:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう 金を返さない時点で
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:10:02.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつらに誠意なんてものは ない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:10.13,default,,0,0,0,,To prove that, I added some weight\Nto the action of kneeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:10.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その証拠に 土下座に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:10.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとした負荷を加えただけで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:14.41,default,,0,0,0,,which made them unable to\Nrender a satisfactory apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう連中は 満足に謝ることも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できなくなる ヒヒ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.30,default,,0,0,0,,They were originally\Nable to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来できるはずなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.41,default,,0,0,0,,If they were truly filled\Nwith remorse,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:24.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当にすまないという気持ちで
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:24.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,胸がいっぱいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:27.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこであれ 土下座ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.65,default,,0,0,0,,they'd have been able\Nto kneel anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.26,default,,0,0,0,,Even if you have to do it\Non a metal plate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:31.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえそれが 肉焦がし 骨焼く
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:33.49,default,,0,0,0,,...that burns the flesh and\Nroasts the bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鉄板の上でもな！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.96,default,,0,0,0,,That is what sincerity\Nis all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:40.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでこそ誠意というもの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.89,0:10:43.56,default,,0,0,0,,Right, Tonegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のう？利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:04.31,default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to explain\Nthis to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前には
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:04.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説明するまでもないんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.02,default,,0,0,0,,but I'll do it just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:07.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一応 念のために言っておく
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:12.54,default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you lower your head\Nfor at least 10 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:12.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この焼き土下座は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:12.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,謝罪する側の誠意の証明として
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:16.52,default,,0,0,0,,...on this burning plate to show\Nyour sincerity in apologising!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:16.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最低10秒は 頭を下げてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:21.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10秒のスタートは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:21.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,額を鉄板に付けた瞬間から
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:21.01,default,,0,0,0,,The time will start when your\Nforehead touches the metal plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:26.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし土下座が
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:26.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10秒に至らない場合は やり直し
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:26.58,default,,0,0,0,,In the event that you can't last\N10 seconds, you'll do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.51,default,,0,0,0,,You'll apologise once more,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:31.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 謝ってもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.77,0:11:31.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始めっからな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.05,default,,0,0,0,,right from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:36.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度でもやる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:39.32,default,,0,0,0,,You'll do it as many times as needed\Nuntil you finish the full 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10秒の土下座が達成されるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:44.50,default,,0,0,0,,The skin and flesh on your\Nforehead will slowly melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:44.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それこそ 額の皮も肉も溶け
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:49.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直接 頭蓋骨を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:49.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焼くことになろうともだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:48.68,default,,0,0,0,,Your skull will also\Nstart to roast...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:53.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハッ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.20,0:11:53.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何もそこまでという顔だな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.67,default,,0,0,0,,You're wondering why\NI'm doing this, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:57.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし こうでなければ いかん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.67,default,,0,0,0,,But this is something\Nthat has to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:02.10,default,,0,0,0,,The value of atonement rises along\Nwith the severity of the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:02.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,謝罪という行為は つらければ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:02.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つらいほど その価値を増す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:08.30,default,,0,0,0,,By enduring the pain, one is\Nable to prove his sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのつらさに耐えてこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,証明できるのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:10.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誠意らしきものを ハハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:14.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できるはずだ 本当にすまないと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:13.99,default,,0,0,0,,He should be able to do it,\Nif he's really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:18.81,default,,0,0,0,,If he's sorry from the bottom\Nof his heart, he will apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,謝りたい気持ちで胸いっぱいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,謝れる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:22.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 謝らずには おれんはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.20,default,,0,0,0,,No, he can't move on\Nwithout apologising.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが カイジ君の友人たちの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.86,0:12:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無念を晴らすことになり
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:27.38,default,,0,0,0,,Your friends will be able to\Nrest in peace then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:32.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同時に 恥をかいた わしへの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:32.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正当な わびにもなろう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:32.21,default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, he can apologise\Nto me for bringing me shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:35.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハ 当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:37.41,default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing is only natural...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:42.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これくらいは当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:42.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誠意とは それほど厳しいのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.91,default,,0,0,0,,Sincerity is going through\Nsuch lengths!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:47.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のう 利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:47.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は示せるよな 誠意を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:46.23,default,,0,0,0,,Right, Tonegawa? You'll\Nshow your sincerity, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:50.42,default,,0,0,0,,Sincerity...\NYour true sincerity...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:51.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当の誠意を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.06,0:12:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フンッ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:58.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり自分からは できぬかの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:58.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:57.08,default,,0,0,0,,So you can't do it\Non your own after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.28,default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ！準備だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:00.13,default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:11.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは実に これが好きでの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:11.08,default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I really like\Nthis contraption!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.15,0:13:16.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,土下座強制機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.35,default,,0,0,0,,The Forced Kneeling\NMachine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてくれ！お願いだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.95,default,,0,0,0,,Please stop this, I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:26.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず返す…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.06,default,,0,0,0,,I'll surely repay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:29.18,default,,0,0,0,,Those insolent people who\Ndon't repay their debts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:31.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金を踏み倒す不心得者を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:31.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この機械に乗せ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:33.22,default,,0,0,0,,...are forced to kneel down\Non top of this machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強引に土下座させる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:41.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが ここまで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:41.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体勢を作っているにも関わらず
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:41.28,default,,0,0,0,,However, if these scoundrels\Nstill refuse to kneel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:44.22,default,,0,0,0,,...after doing so much to\Nget them into position,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:44.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ土下座に至らない不心得者は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:47.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強引に誠意を実行させる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.18,default,,0,0,0,,they are forced to show\Ntheir sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:51.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとなしくしていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:51.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焼かれるのは額だけで済むが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:51.39,default,,0,0,0,,If they behave properly,\Nonly the forehead is roasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:54.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暴れるから 顔中を焼かれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:54.37,default,,0,0,0,,If they struggle,\Nthe whole face is roasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もん絶… 失禁する
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:57.09,default,,0,0,0,,They faint and even\Nwet their pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:11.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ やってもらおうかのう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:11.25,default,,0,0,0,,It's about time for you\Nto do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:14.80,default,,0,0,0,,Let's start the Roasting\NKneeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.34,0:14:16.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スタートだ 焼き土下座
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:21.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,触るな！わしに指一本触れるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.61,default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!\NDon't lay a finger on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.08,default,,0,0,0,,It's alright if I do it myself,\Nright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人でやれば問題なかろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:24.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人で…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:24.50,default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒヒヒヒ もちろんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.22,0:14:30.79,default,,0,0,0,,Of course. That's the most\Nideal option.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:31.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:31.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが いちばん望ましい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ しかし 利根川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も知ってるように
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.57,default,,0,0,0,,However, Tonegawa,\Nas you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:37.07,default,,0,0,0,,nobody has been able\Nto kneel continuously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この焼き土下座を10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自力で やり続けた者は いない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:40.31,default,,0,0,0,,...for 10 seconds\Nby their own ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:44.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり無理しない方が
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:44.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身のためだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:43.91,default,,0,0,0,,It's to your benefit\Nif you don't overdo things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:49.00,default,,0,0,0,,If you fail, your face will be\Nroasted numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:49.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失敗すると
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:49.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度も顔を焼くことになるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:53.57,default,,0,0,0,,Sizzle, sizzle, sizzle!\NSizzle away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:57.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どけろ その機械をどけろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:57.39,default,,0,0,0,,Move aside!\NMove away from the machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヒ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:25.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エヘ… エヘ… イヒヒヒ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:32.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:31.91,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:02.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,永遠に思える10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:02.39,default,,0,0,0,,The 10 seconds felt like\Nforever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:06.55,default,,0,0,0,,During those 10 seconds,\Na dreadful smell gradually emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:07.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あびきょうかん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:07.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異臭と 阿鼻叫喚の中 続く10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.96,default,,0,0,0,,An unending nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:10.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚めない悪夢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆえつ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪魔の愉悦 地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:13.08,default,,0,0,0,,The devil's enjoyment...\NAn abyss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:20.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ まだ４秒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.69,default,,0,0,0,,It's only been 4 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:33.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川… 利根川…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.84,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa... Tonegawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:37.91,default,,0,0,0,,Impossible... What's\Nwith these tears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:36.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばかな… 何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:41.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何の涙だ くそっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.76,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:45.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:51.48,default,,0,0,0,,In the end, Tonegawa managed to\Nlast 12 seconds on the hot plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:51.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 利根川は この生き地獄を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:51.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,12秒やりおおし 果てる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:57.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりおおした後は しばらく動けず
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:57.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,患部を冷やし タオルで治療後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:54.66,default,,0,0,0,,He was unable to move\Nfor a while after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:57.33,default,,0,0,0,,and had cold towels applied\Nto his injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:17:01.05,default,,0,0,0,,He was later able to stand\Nwith some support, and left...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肩を借りながら やっと立ち上がり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,退室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:05.30,default,,0,0,0,,In any case, Tonegawa\Nwas able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:05.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 利根川は やりおおした
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焼き土下座を！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.90,default,,0,0,0,,He was able to perform\Nthe Roasting Kneel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:14.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハアアア… アヒ… アアア…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:24.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.62,default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:24.61,default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.06,default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:29.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:29.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違っていたって 何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.29,default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:33.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川は本当の敵じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:33.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かいらいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:33.30,default,,0,0,0,,Tonegawa isn't our real enemy.\NHe's just a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:38.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつも俺たちと同じように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:38.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ 利用されてきただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.50,default,,0,0,0,,He was just being made use of,\Njust like we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:42.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男 会長だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.57,default,,0,0,0,,That man...\NThe director...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長を倒さなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:47.12,default,,0,0,0,,Ishida and the rest won't be avenged\Nuntil I've beaten the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さんたちの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵をとったことには ならない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:51.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな気持ちも分からないでは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:51.96,default,,0,0,0,,Well... It's not that I don't\Nunderstand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.12,default,,0,0,0,,But we can't do anything\Nabout it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも それは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しょうがないっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は勝ってねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:57.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ってねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:57.32,default,,0,0,0,,I have yet to win!\NI haven't won!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなこと ないっすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:01.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,十分 勝ってるじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:01.04,default,,0,0,0,,That's not the case!\NYou've won quite a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこその この金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.18,default,,0,0,0,,That's why you have\Nall that money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:09.66,default,,0,0,0,,That's just the fee for staging\Na performance for the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:09.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 会長のためのショーを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:09.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,演じた出演料 ギャラだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャラで いいじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金は金っすよ 変わりません
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:11.94,default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with it\Nbeing a fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.14,default,,0,0,0,,It's still money.\NThat fact doesn't change!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんだって 金のために
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,闘ってきたんじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:17.20,default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you come this far\Nfor money as well, Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う… 金は半分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:20.19,default,,0,0,0,,No! Half of it was\Nfor the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:24.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は金だけでなく 何というか…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.16,default,,0,0,0,,but I didn't do it just\Nfor that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.71,default,,0,0,0,,How do I put it...\NI wanted to defeat the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:28.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,倒したかったんだ 敵を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:29.85,default,,0,0,0,,The enemy...\NIn other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:33.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり できることなら その金を
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:32.65,default,,0,0,0,,I would use that money\Nif I have the ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:36.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度 全てを賭けて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:37.99,default,,0,0,0,,I would bet it all once again and\Nhave a face-off with that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの男と…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってるんですか！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.52,default,,0,0,0,,Please stop it!\NWhat are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金 もう 奇跡的っていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天井ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:44.30,default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, getting this\Nmoney is a miracle in itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも この先 更に勝負して
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:50.76,default,,0,0,0,,Or do you mean that you have\Na plan to win yet another bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:50.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ算段っていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.55,0:18:50.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝算でもあるんですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ない…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:51.80,default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.39,0:18:54.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ やめてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.61,default,,0,0,0,,Then please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうせ カイジさんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たんまり 借金あるんでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:58.95,default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you have\Na huge debt, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:02.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この金は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:02.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを返して やり直す金
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:02.75,default,,0,0,0,,This money is for you\Nto repay your debts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.37,default,,0,0,0,,and to start all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:06.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一か八か勝負する金じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:06.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないでしょ？違いますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.44,default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:09.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ そうだけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.47,default,,0,0,0,,Well, you are right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:11.13,default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:13.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんだけど… くそっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:13.49,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 カイジは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しぶしぶ 矛を収める
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:18.96,default,,0,0,0,,In the end, Kaiji reluctantly gave\Nup the idea against his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかたなく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だあっ… うう… ああっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:26.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ カイジさん！タ… タオル！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:24.90,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:26.91,default,,0,0,0,,Get a towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:30.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう ないんすよ さっき
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:30.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川が冷やすのに使って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:30.73,default,,0,0,0,,There's no more left! They were used\Nto help cool Tonegawa down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:33.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ ティッシュを大量に！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:33.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ は はい！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.47,default,,0,0,0,,Then go get some tissue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:33.14,default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:39.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ばか！貸せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.52,default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, pass that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しみるかもしれませんが…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.96,default,,0,0,0,,This may hurt a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救急箱を借りてきました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.19,default,,0,0,0,,I managed to find\Na first-aid box!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:53.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジの耳の傷… その応急処置…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:53.43,default,,0,0,0,,The bleeding from Kaiji's\Nwound was finally stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:57.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とりあえずの止血…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.43,default,,0,0,0,,thanks to the first-aid\Ntreatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:01.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと 不格好ですけど…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:20:01.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.42,default,,0,0,0,,It may look a bit odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:00.82,default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:05.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行きましょう 病院に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:05.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,耳 今なら くっつきますよ きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:03.33,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.33,0:20:05.68,default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they can still\Nreattach your ear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:09.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… みんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.41,default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いろいろ ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:14.92,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:18.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんすか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.65,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:20.15,default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NThis is to be expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:20.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これくらい当然ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たち本当に うれしかったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一矢 報いてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:23.93,default,,0,0,0,,We were elated that you\Nmanaged to stand up for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですよ カイジさん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.99,0:20:26.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うれしかったんですから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:27.43,default,,0,0,0,,You really did it!\NKaiji, you were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すっと しましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.35,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:33.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.17,default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:40.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから もう帰りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.78,default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:00.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.16,0:20:59.10,default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.26,default,,0,0,0,,At that point...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,引っかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:09.40,default,,0,0,0,,Something flashed across\NKaiji's mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よぎる… カイジに「何か」！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長を倒しうる「何か」が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:18.35,default,,0,0,0,,A plan to defeat the director!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:45.30,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Heresy.
